# Bytes are bytes (18_windows_port program decision 9): the core never
# normalizes line endings, fixtures may be deliberately CRLF or mixed,
# and byte-stability tests compare working-tree files verbatim. Disable
# git's eol conversion for every path so a checkout is byte-identical
# on every platform regardless of the machine's core.autocrlf. Without
# this, autocrlf=true (the Git for Windows default) smudges fixtures to
# CRLF and the canvas byte-stability suite fails on Windows.
* -text

demo-vault/.obsidian/themes/** binary
demo-vault/attachments/*.mp3 binary
demo-vault/attachments/*.pdf binary
demo-vault/attachments/*.png binary
